---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Gas Station NNN Investments — Bonus Depreciation | STAX Real Estate" description="Gas station NNN investments with 100% bonus depreciation in income-tax-free states. Long-term leases, recession-resistant income, and Year 1 write-offs. Sourced by an operator-broker.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="pt-[140px] pb-[80px] px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <div>
        <span class="inline-block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red bg-red-light px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded mb-5">
          For NNN Investors
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl lg:text-[52px] leading-[1.12] font-semibold text-black mb-6 tracking-tight">
          100% Bonus Depreciation. Gas Stations Are the Last Great Tax Shelter.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-9 max-w-[520px]">
          Cost segregation on gas station improvements lets investors write off nearly the entire purchase price in Year 1. No other NNN asset class offers this — and we source deals from operators who trust us because we've been in their shoes.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-red text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md text-[15px] font-semibold hover:bg-red-dark transition-colors tracking-wide">
            Schedule a Consultation
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-[18px] h-[18px]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/deals" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-black transition-colors">
            See current deals →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative h-[400px] lg:h-[480px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-gray-100">
        <img src="/images/sunoco-porsche.png" alt="Premium Gas Station NNN Investment Property" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm px-8 py-6 flex gap-10 border-t border-black/5">
          <div>
            <div class="font-heading text-[28px] font-bold text-red">100%</div>
            <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mt-0.5">Yr 1 Write-Off</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-heading text-[28px] font-bold text-black">$0</div>
            <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mt-0.5">State Income Tax</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-heading text-[28px] font-bold text-black">15-25</div>
            <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mt-0.5">Year Leases</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE TAX PLAY -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12 bg-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red mb-4">The Tax Play</div>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-[40px] font-semibold text-black mb-5 tracking-tight leading-snug">
        Why smart investors are buying gas stations right now
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700 max-w-[640px] mb-12">
        Gas stations and c-stores combine recession-resistant cash flow with the most aggressive tax benefits in commercial real estate.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="rounded-xl p-8 bg-white border border-black/8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-light flex items-center justify-center mb-5 text-red text-xl font-bold">
            100%
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-[22px] font-semibold text-black mb-3">Bonus Depreciation</h3>
          <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700">Cost segregation on canopies, tanks, pumps, paving, and signage means investors can write off the vast majority of the purchase price in Year 1. The OBBB Act made this possible for real property.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl p-8 bg-white border border-black/8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-light flex items-center justify-center mb-5 text-red text-xl font-bold">
            1031
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-[22px] font-semibold text-black mb-3">1031 Exchange Ready</h3>
          <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700">Roll gains from another property into a gas station NNN deal and defer 100% of capital gains. Single tenant, long lease, clear title — ideal 1031 targets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl p-8 bg-white border border-black/8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-light flex items-center justify-center mb-5 text-red text-xl font-bold">
            $0
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-[22px] font-semibold text-black mb-3">Income-Tax-Free States</h3>
          <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700">Florida, Texas, Nevada, Tennessee — no state income tax. Pair with federal bonus depreciation for a tax shelter that's hard to beat in any asset class.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY STAX FOR INVESTORS -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red mb-4">The STAX Advantage</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-[40px] font-semibold text-black mb-6 tracking-tight leading-snug">
          Off-market access from a broker operators actually trust
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-8">
          The best gas station deals never hit the open market. They come from operators who want to sell to someone who understands their business. That's where STAX has an edge no institutional NNN firm can match.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red"></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-1">Operator-Sourced Deal Flow</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Off-market opportunities from our operator network. Not on LoopNet, not through national NNN firms.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red"></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-1">Real Operational Due Diligence</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Gallonage, fuel margin, environmental risk, brand contracts, c-store performance. We've owned and operated these businesses — we know what to look for.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red"></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-1">Tax Strategy From Day One</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Cost segregation, 1031 timing, entity optimization — built into every deal from the start, not bolted on after.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="h-[500px] rounded-xl bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-gray-500">
        [ Investment Property / NNN Image ]
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DEAL ALERTS -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12 bg-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto">
      <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase text-red mb-4">Deal Alerts</div>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-[40px] font-semibold text-black mb-5 tracking-tight leading-snug">
        Get first look at gas station NNN deals
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-12">
        Tell us your criteria and we'll send matching opportunities — including off-market deals from our operator network. Full financials, lease terms, and depreciation analysis included.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-12 border border-black/8">
        <form class="space-y-6">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Full Name</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-black/10 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red/50 transition" placeholder="Your name" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Email Address</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-black/10 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red/50 transition" placeholder="you@example.com" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <label for="budget" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Investment Range</label>
              <select id="budget" name="budget" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-black/10 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red/50 transition bg-white">
                <option value="">Select range</option>
                <option value="1-3m">$1M – $3M</option>
                <option value="3-5m">$3M – $5M</option>
                <option value="5-10m">$5M – $10M</option>
                <option value="10m+">$10M+</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="interest" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Primary Interest</label>
              <select id="interest" name="interest" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-black/10 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red/50 transition bg-white">
                <option value="">Select interest</option>
                <option value="bonus-dep">Bonus Depreciation</option>
                <option value="1031">1031 Exchange</option>
                <option value="passive-income">Passive NNN Income</option>
                <option value="portfolio">Portfolio Building</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-red text-white font-semibold py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-dark transition-colors">
            Get Deal Alerts
          </button>
        </form>
        <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-600 mt-6">Matching deals only — no spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-black to-[#1a1a2e] py-20 px-6 lg:px-12 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-[640px] mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Ready to invest in gas station NNN?</h2>
      <p class="text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-white/60 mb-8">Let's discuss your criteria, tax situation, and timeline. First consultation is free — principal to principal.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-red text-white px-9 py-4 rounded-md text-[15px] font-semibold hover:bg-red-dark transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Consultation
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-[18px] h-[18px]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
